This paper discusses the future of cellular technology and its integration with other wireless technologies, which falls under the category of network and communication technologies (cs.NI). It also discusses the need for spectrum regulation and energy and cost efficiencies, which are topics related to information theory (cs.IT) and computer networks (cs.COMM). The paper also mentions the use of massive numbers of antennas, which is a topic related to applied mathematics (cs.AR) and machine learning (cs.MA).
